source: Coafura, machiajul, manichiura, vestimentaţia, accesoriile, zâmbetul, carisma, toate au întregit paleta celor care au râvnit la titlul de Miss Boboc.
target: Hairdo, makeup, manicure, attire, accessories, smile, charisma—all completed the range of those who aspired to the title of Miss Freshman.
